import { Switch, Route } from "react-router-dom"
import { ContactConfirm } from "../Pages/ContactConfirm"
import { FrontPage } from "../Pages/FrontPage"

export const IndexRouter = () => {
  return(
  <Switch>
    <Route path='/'>
      <FrontPage />
    </Route>
    <Route path='/contactConfirm'>
        <ContactConfirm />
    </Route>
  </Switch>

  )
}
